*grep*(1),
*strip*(1),
*packages*(7),
*packaging*(7)

# CAVEATS

Use _.nostrip_ sparingly.
Preserving debug symbols increases package size and may reduce
reproducibility, as debug sections vary across toolchains and builds.
Restrict exceptions to debugging tools or cases where stripping breaks
functionality.

